        <p><span class="contact-info">Data controller:</span> A. Filmore Publishing SRL, Belgium</p>
        <p><span class="contact-info">Contact:</span> aleksfilmore@gmail.com</p>

        <h2>2. What data we collect & why</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Data</th>
                    <th>When collected</th>
                    <th>Purpose</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Email address</td>
                    <td>When you subscribe or request a bonus chapter</td>
