        <h2>3. Legal bases (GDPR Art. 6)</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Consent</strong> – you actively opt-in before receiving emails.</li>
            <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> – minimal, anonymised analytics to keep the site functional and secure.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. How we use your data</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Deliver the requested bonus chapter and future newsletters (2-4 emails / month).</li>
            <li>Announce new books, promotions, events.</li>
            <li>Measure open and click rates to improve email content and timing.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. How we store & secure data</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Mailing list is hosted on MailerLite / Kit / other GDPR-compliant ESP (EU servers or Standard Contractual Clauses).</li>
            <li>Access limited to Aleks Filmore and one trusted assistant, protected by strong passwords and 2-factor authentication.</li>
            <li>No personal data is ever sold or rented.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Retention periods</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Email data: kept until you unsubscribe or request deletion.</li>
            <li>Analytics logs: retained 26 months, then anonymised or deleted automatically.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Sharing & processors</h2>
        <p>We share data only with trusted service providers that process it on our behalf and under strict confidentiality:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email service provider (MailerLite / Kit).</li>
            <li>Cloud storage (e.g., Dropbox or Google Drive) only if you click an external download link.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>All processors are GDPR-compliant.</p>

        <h2>8. Your rights (EU GDPR)</h2>
        <p>As a data subject under the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the following rights:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access the personal data we hold on you.</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data.</li>
            <li>Erase your data (“right to be forgotten”).</li>
            <li>Restrict or object to processing.</li>
            <li>Data portability.</li>
            <li>Lodge a complaint with the Belgian Data Protection Authority.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Email <span class="contact-info">aleksfilmore@gmail.com</span> with any request; we’ll respond within 30 days.</p>

        <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>If we change how we handle personal data, we’ll update this page. Material changes will be announced by email.</p>
